title: @OspreyMGolf Tie for 7th at Tavistock Collegiate Invitational
text: @OspreyMGolf Tie for 7th at Tavistock Collegiate Invitational North Florida Athletics Final Results (pdf) WINDERMERE, Fla. -- Playing in a field that included eight Top 50 squads, the No. 60 North Florida men's golf team earned a tie for seventh in the competitive Tavistock Collegiate Invitational played at Isleworth Country Club (par 72 / 7,544 yards).The Ospreys finished with a three-day total of 883, matching the score of No. 51 Texas Tech. UNF, who collected their second straight Top 10 showing, struggled in the final round shooting a 12-under 300 on Tuesday."Not the finish we were looking for after two good days to start," said head coach . "We were really competitive with a bunch of schools ranked in the Top 30, so that was good to see. Unfortunately, we made too many small mistakes that prevented us from having a much better finish."Senior
